WEBVTT

00:06:58.800 --> 00:07:01.700
Nimekua nikifanya hivi
miaka nane iliopita.

00:07:02.760 --> 00:07:06.176
Idadi kubwa ya watu
ninaowafuata wanakubali kukutana nami.

00:07:06.200 --> 00:07:07.536
Wengi wao ni wanaume,

00:07:07.560 --> 00:07:09.390
lakini nimekutana pia na wanawake.

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:13.896
Nimefanya kama kanuni
kukutana nyumbani kwao daima

00:07:13.920 --> 00:07:16.320
kuonyesha kwa nje kua
ninawaamini.

00:07:16.960 --> 00:07:20.776
Naleta chakula mara kwa mara
kwa sababu tunapokula pamoja,

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:23.216
ni rahisi kujua
nini tunacho cha kufanana

00:07:23.240 --> 00:07:25.120
na kuwa na amani kwa pamoja.

00:07:26.480 --> 00:07:30.896
Pamoja na njia hii, nimejifunza
mafunzo ya thamani.